	<h1 class="title">泄密事件上升为恐怖袭击威胁，索尼已缴械</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/73/small/73.jpg?1415670876" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">俞斯译</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-12-18 17:08:10 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/4521/medium/4521.jpg?1436649798" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


